"Perhaps in terms of the number of papers needed for tax returns we are in the first place worldwide," comments Karel Havl<0xC3><0xAD><0xC4><0x8D>ek of the Association of Small and Medium-sized Enterprises and Entrepreneurs of the Czech Republic.
