Anyone can indicate some administrative or bureaucratic absurdity every year between April and the end of September, when the contest closes.
Submissions can be made on the website www.firmaroku.cz. The contest organizer then selects seven candidates for the "anti-award" and, during October, allows the public to vote on the Internet through www.firmaroku.cz/absurdita and www.ihned.cz.
It wins the absurdity that gets the most votes.
